{"tid":1564554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵偽非官方機構宣布：搭輕鐵唔使錢！","createTime":"2019-09-12T22:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T08:14:07.000Z","uid":141675,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"24be0e4316c77f1c6944a1ec1ebe573a9572cfa4","tid":1564554,"uid":141675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:54:15.000Z","msg":"輕鐵站設施早前同樣受示威活動、後續的警務行動影響而受損<br />\n<br />\n維修人員會先安排設施暫停服務，再將機內零件集中至較繁忙的輕鐵站，俾果度嘅票務機、八達通收費器繼續開機 🔧<br />\n<br />\n🧡 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果「入站」收費器未能運作，或情況所需時，乘客可先登車而毋須費時排隊<br />\n</span></span><br />\n💚 無法喺「出站」收費器拍卡時，則可到輕鐵客務中心退款<br />\n<br />\n🛍 大家都可以去鄰近的便利店增值八達通<br />\n<br />\n－<br />\n<br />\nFacilities at Light Rail stops have also been damaged by previous protests and the police actions thereafter<br />\n<br />\nTechnicians will first put these facilities out of service and consolidate the parts inside and keep Ticket Machines and Octopus Validators operating at busier stops<br />\n<br />\n🧡 Join any trains first if &ldquo;Entry&rdquo; validators are out of service or it is essential to do so<br />\n<br />\n💚 Visit a Light Rail Customer Service Centre if you&rsquo;re unable to touch &ldquo;Exit&rdquo; validators<br />\n<br />\n🛍 Top-up your Octopus at a convenience store nearby<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/13/065333_28057405bea5b1ee1184188f3dcaf93d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F13%2F065333_28057405bea5b1ee1184188f3dcaf93d.jpeg&h=5eaebb3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/188207124523573/posts/3280013415342913?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F188207124523573%2Fposts%2F3280013415342913%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=81468e68\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/188207124523573/posts/3280013415342913?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"74672dfdd5060b5814f982c3cfebbfc2ba42de84","tid":1564554,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:54:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"b8903a77a098f43c62a9fcbc1c12831c99b741f3","tid":1564554,"uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:57:11.000Z","msg":"全呢拆機<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a2a2105f4db03e577c2ed2bdc969dc47446861","tid":1564554,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:05:03.000Z","msg":"希望你可以幫我share呢篇文, 我知呢篇文好長, 如果唔想睇曬既話入黎睇下堆subheading都好, 我好有信心呢篇文係可以幫助打破現況 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"021cc4b0e1a71c6c23c74dd5d5b666a6bf6714c1","tid":1564554,"uid":141675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:06:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">手足！你地無做錯到！ </span></span>"},{"pid":"922b5b7e480fa9c955fdb6cca661b544c140c556","tid":1564554,"uid":62226,"like":1,"dislike":0,